  <body onload="prettyPrint()">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>This is just for test purposes. This is not ample final version</h1>
      <h2>A light and responsive front-end framework</h2>

      <h3>Buttons</h3>
      <div>
        <a class="button" href="#">Default</a>
        <a class="primary button" href="#">Primary</a>
        <a class="disabled button" href="#">Disabled</a>
      </div>
      <p>Need button states? I got you covered:</p>
      <div>
        <a class="info button" href="#">Info</a>
        <a class="success button" href="#">Success</a>
        <a class="warning button" href="#">Warning</a>
        <a class="danger button" href="#">Danger</a>
      </div>
<pre class="prettyprint lang-html"><code>
&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;button&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Default&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;primary button&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Primary&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;disabled button&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Disabled&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;info button&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Info&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;success button&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Success&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;warning button&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Warning&lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;a class=&quot;danger button&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Danger&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>

      <h3>Grid</h3>
      <p>Ample use a 12 columns grid system so you can to things like this:<p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
        <div class="one column"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="three columns"></div>
        <div class="two columns"></div>
        <div class="seven columns"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="six columns"></div>
        <div class="six columns"></div>
      </div>
<pre class="prettyprint lang-html"><code>
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one column&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;three columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;two columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;seven columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;six columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;six columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
