      <p>You need more? What about centering and nesting colums?</p>
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="three columns"></div>
        <div class="one columns"></div>
        <div class="three columns"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="four columns"></div>
        <div class="two columns"></div>
        <div class="four columns" style="background-color: transparent;">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="four columns"></div>
            <div class="two columns"></div>
            <div class="four columns"></div>
            <div class="two columns"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="two columns"></div>
      </div>
<pre class="prettyprint lang-html"><code>
&lt;div class=&quot;row centered&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;three columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;three columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;four columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;two columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;four columns&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;four columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;two columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;four columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;two columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;two columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>

      <p>Sometimes is also useful to align things. Give it a try!</p>
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="three columns floated left"></div>
        <div class="one columns"></div>
        <div class="three columns floated right"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="three columns floated left"></div>
        <div class="three columns floated right"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="four columns"></div>
        <div class="two columns"></div>
        <div class="three columns"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="right aligned row">
        <div class="three columns"></div>
        <div class="two columns"></div>
        <div class="four columns"></div>
      </div>
<pre class="prettyprint lang-html"><code>
&lt;div class=&quot;row centered&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;three columns floated left&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;one columns&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;three columns floated right&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;three columns floated left&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
